    "body": "Oh, I see. Sorry, I thought you didn't understand what was going on.\r\n\r\nYes, unfortunately, you need to use it like that. I think in the meantime, we can detect that error when loading the config, and replace it for something clearer. If you feel like sending a PR doing this, I can give you pointers.\r\n\r\nAdding support for ESM is more complex than it seems, as ESM doesn't evaluate imported modules in order, whereas CJS does, and our plugin system depends on that. So it needs a breaking change, and not a small one.",
